               <p>Prisoner's defence. I went in to buy a loaf, and<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179810240028"></xptr>dropped thres halfpence behind the counter; I thought no harm in going round to pick them up, and Mrs. Baker caught me there.</p>
